Class MTDLineParser

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class MTDLineParser
extends MZTabLineParser
    Parse a metadata line into a element. Metadata Element start with MTD, its structure like: MTD MetadataElement([id])(-MetadataProperty) {Element Value}
